# AGENTS.md

This is the canonical, tool-neutral instruction file for [[ project_name ]]. Every
coding agent (Codex, Cursor, Copilot, Windsurf, Zed, Aider, Claude Code, Gemini
CLI, and the rest) reads this file natively or through a one-line bridge. It is
the spine of how work happens here. Read it at the start of every session.

